Hi mykou.<br />I'm bad. Sorry, <br />I should have modded a simple glass color masked skin for you.<br />Thing about Metro skin, is it follows Windows 8 startscreen/10 system color, not glass color.<br />To change color, would take awhile to figure out. A lot of people have done it though.<br />Can alter all the dark1/dark2 shade's text in skin file, and put as darker dark2/dark3.<br /><br />Or if you don't want any color at all,<br />here is dark grey sample. There will still be a small amount of glass color showing through.<br />To get rid of it, in CSM settings, set &quot;Override glass color &quot; to black, <br />or set Glass opacity to 0.<br /><br />OK, over to you to play, and turn into your personal preferences.<br />I shutupa my face hole for rest of today. <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> — Sat Jun 24, 2017 5:13 pm</p><hr />
