<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7703&amp;p=33128#p33128"><![CDATA[
clrSharp2 Glass revB.skin has menu floating at bottom.<br /><br /><br />The classic Metro.skin could be modified to have it float.<br /><br />Increase menu bitmap size to include invisible portion (0 alpha)<br />Increase the bitmap dimension slices to match new size.<br />Increase main padding, to push the text further down.<br />Increase padding for name /user picture.<br /><br />Here is simple example Metro Float.skin to learn from, and personalize your way.<br />Only two column has float option. <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_e_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br />I did not test every <strike>funtion</strike>. function.<br />I did not check for spelling mistakes.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> — Sat Jun 24, 2017 12:15 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
